# GitHub Issues

- Use `gh` for all GitHub issue operations — never the web UI or undocumented APIs.
- Use only the label vocabulary in `.agents/docs/triage-labels.md`.
- External PRs are not a triage surface — do not treat them as issues to label or groom.
- When a skill says "publish to the issue tracker", create a GitHub issue via `gh issue create`.
- Full command reference: `.agents/docs/issue-tracker.md`.
